<item>
            <title>[LU-311] Wiki build instructions not updated for CentOS-5.6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-311</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The detailed instructions for building lustre on CentOS (on the wiki) needs to be updated for CentOS-5.6 (kernel ...-238)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently the step by step instructions will break since b1_8 now requires the ...-238 kernel&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At least the following needs to be done:&lt;br/&gt;
1) kernel src.rpm mentioned and used&lt;br/&gt;
2) wrong .config is copied (should now be lustre/kernel_patches/kernel_configs/kernel-2.6.18-2.6-rhel5-x86_64.config)&lt;br/&gt;
3) title explicitly mentiones CentOS-5.5 ...&lt;/p&gt;</description>
